<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an König Ruprecht I.</head><p>Der Rat kündigt Hans Maurer, Diener der Stadt, wegen eines zum Ewiglicht von St. Egidien zu Nürnberg gehörigen Guts zu Großhabersdorf an, das Wirich von Treuchtlingen zu Lehen geht und er vor das königliche Hofgericht geladen hat.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_160" id="78v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_160_r1l1">Künig </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_160_r1l2">Gnedıger fürſte vnd <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> / Als wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> durchleuhtikeit </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_160_r1l3">voꝛmals <expan>verſchrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd 
<del rend="strikethrough">gebeten <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> bı </del> den hanſen <expan>Mawr<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_160_r1l4"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> dıener cʒu <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>künigkl<ex>ichen</ex></expan> <expan>gnade<ex>n</ex></expan> geſant <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> von </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_160_r1l5">des guts wegen cʒu hadmanſtorff / das 
<del rend="strikethrough">her </del> cʒu <expan>eine<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan cert="low">ymm<ex>er</ex>liht</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_160_r1l6">hie in dem gotſhauſe cʒu ſant Egıdien gehört / vnd das </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_160_r1l7">her wirich von <expan>Treuhtling<ex>en</ex></expan> cʒu lehen <expan>empfange<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd für </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_160_r1l8"><expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> künigklıch hofgerihte geladen hat / Alſo ſenden wir <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_160_r1l9">darümb cʒu <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>künigklıch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> gnaden den <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> diener </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_160_r1l10">vnd <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> / vvaʒ derſelb ~ <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> diener in <expan>derſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ſache </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_160_r1l11">cʒu diſem mal an ewr <expan>durchl<ex>euhtikeit</ex></expan> werb von <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> etc </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_160_r1l12">vt in <expan>for<ex>ma</ex></expan> / <expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> in die <expan>ſ<ex>an</ex>c<ex>t</ex>i</expan> Erhardi Anno Nono </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_160" id="78v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Künig </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Gnediger fürste und <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, als wir
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> durchleuhtikeit vormals
                                <expan>verschrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und den Hansen
                                <expan>Mawr<ex>er</ex></expan>, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
                        diener, czu <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>künigkl<ex>ichen</ex></expan>
<expan>gnade<ex>n</ex></expan> gesant <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> von des
                        guts wegen czu Hadmanstorff, das czu <expan>eine<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>ymm<ex>er</ex>liht</expan> hie in dem gotshause czu sant
                        Egidien gehört und das her Wirich von <expan>Treuhtling<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        czu lehen <expan>empfange<ex>n</ex></expan> und für
                            <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> künigklich hofgerihte geladen hat. Also
                        senden wir <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> darümb czu
                            <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>künigklich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> gnaden den
                            <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan>, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
                        diener, und <expan>ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, waz derselb
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> diener in
                            <expan>derselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> sache czu disem mal an ewr
                                <expan>durchl<ex>euhtikeit</ex></expan> werb von
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> etc. ut in <expan>for<ex>ma</ex></expan>.
                                <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> in die
                            <expan>s<ex>an</ex>c<ex>t</ex>i</expan> Erhardi anno nono.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
